{
  "stem": "20035.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean we lived in a-- in a-- in a total, total ignorance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the only thing, what we could-- could visualize, that Hungarians are not going to allow anything-- anything worse then.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we go to a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember at that time, already, dad was telling us that both of us, thank goodness.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you see that the education and the upbringing, what you get, that we had to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had to-- I mean, including physical work in our store, we had to do, both of us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Especially summertime.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were like-- like any other employee who had to carry the 50 or 75-pound bag on their shoulder like anybody else.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That thank goodness you're in good physical and strength.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And don't worry about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You will be able to work like anybody else, like I am.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, dad was saying it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And grandpa will stay with mom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That was the-- that was the worst, what we could-- what we could visualize. till it came the day, probably it was beginning of May.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Suddenly they herded us up to the railroad station, where we were shoved into railroad cars, to cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- the whole family of mine and an awful lot of-- I mean, including a couple of uncles and aunts and cousins and friends.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And basically, our very close-- I knew everybody at that train, everybody in that car.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, there wasn't a stranger in that car who we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the first time when I felt what human dignity is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, you know, you are 15 and a 1/2.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My brother was almost 18.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You are a brash, young, Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Know-it-all.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Normal.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think so it's normal, after my three kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
